{
  "stem": "24231.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So we-- we got on that wagon and just drove the horses at night towards Prague.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- the Germans, the Germans, what happened is the Germans packed up some of the horses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had-- I think we had maybe 10 pair of horses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the horses which I had were older pair of horses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because as I said, my uncle was in charge.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some of the horses were really thrifty.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he didn't want me to get hurt with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he gave me older horses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These horses were maybe like 12 years-- 12 years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they were not as thrifty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the Germans didn't take those horses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The majority of the horses, they take.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they packed up before the Russians came in, loaded up whatever they had and just-- just cleaned out of the-- or they disappeared from there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was really nobody in charge of-- of the-- of the people in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- they completely disappeared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we just packed up and went-- went to Prague.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the way--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Me, my father, my sister and two friends, we went to Prague.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we traveled at night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We bumped into Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They gave us marmalade.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Somewhere they stole-- stole somewhere barrels of marmalade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Gave us marmalade, they gave us some food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we traveled throughout the whole night from Theresienstadt to Prague.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as I mentioned previously, as we were approaching our home, it's like an-- a street going up, a long street going up towards our house, the people started to recognize my-- my father, some of these.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this word spread around that the Taussig family is coming-- coming home.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
